-- Bankers' Association's Knight Appointed CEO of Energy UK
-- B y   H a n n a h   B e n j a m i n
-- 2012-05-12T12:48:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-12/bankers-association-s-knight-appointed-ceo-of-energy-uk.html
Angela Knight , chief executive
officer of the British Bankers’ Association, has been appointed
CEO of  Energy UK , according to a statement on the trade
association’s website.  She will take up the post at the energy-industry trade
association after she steps down from her role at the BBA at the
end of July, according to the  statement .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Hannah Benjamin in London at 
